data.title: Units
data.text: We are the 136th Airlift Wing, Texas Air National Guard, the premier airlift team of choice. We are located in the heartland of North Texas, just outside of downtown Fort Worth. The wing is collocated with the Navy, Marines, Air Force Reserve and Army at Naval Air Station Fort Worth Joint Reserve Base (NAS Fort Worth JRB), Carswell Field. The wing is comprised of five groups, 19 units and one geographically separated unit (GSU). We are Texans serving Texas. We are ready to answer our Nation's call anywhere, anytime. Nulli Secundus!
